summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2201, for the improvement of Fifth Avenue North, from Harrison Street to Aloha Street and Aloha Street from Fifth Avenue North to Taylor Avenue, all in the City of Seattle, by planking the same, by constructing curbs and gutters, temporary plank walks and provisions for the surface drainage on Fifth Avenue North from Harrison Street to Roy Street, under Ordinance No. 22113, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
